import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import './Styles/Navbar.css' import Nav from '../Assets/icons8-menu-64.png' function Navbar() { const [toggle,settoggle] = useState(true) function toggler() { if (toggle){ settoggle(false) } else{ settoggle(true) } } return (
    Home
    Products
      Catalog
      Gallery
      Tesimonials
    About Us
    Contact
    Login
{`${(toggle)? 'Menu':'Close'}`}
                  ) } export default Navbar
